-- TAKE A LOOK-Malaysia says jet crashed in sea; weather halts search
-- 
-- Tue Mar 25, 2014 02:31AM EDT
-- None



March 25 (Reuters) -    Bad weather and rough seas forced the suspension of the search for any wreckage of a missing Malaysian jetliner that officials are now sure crashed in the remote Indian Ocean with the loss of all 239 aboard.

